    N6["6. Commit or output: bridge event | escrow mutation | relay evidence"]
    N7["7. Consumption: watcher-sol | gateway | shared bridge"]
    N8["8. Operation: source event, confirmations, message hash, cursor, submit hash, and final state"]
    N1 --> N2
    N2 --> N3
